#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.106"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.106:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.106:0.2"
msgid "10. Ānisaṃsavagga "
msgstr "10. Benefit "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.106:0.3"
msgid "106. Taṇhāsutta "
msgstr "106. Craving "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.445, sc1
msgctxt "an6.106:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, taṇhā pahātabbā, tayo ca mānā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should give up these three cravings and three conceits. "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso taṇhā pahātabbā? "
msgstr "What three cravings should you give up? "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.3"
msgid "Kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā—"
msgstr "Craving for sensual pleasures, craving for continued existence, and craving to end existence. "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.4"
msgid "imā tisso taṇhā pahātabbā. "
msgstr "These are the three cravings you should give up. "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.5"
msgid "Katame tayo mānā pahātabbā? "
msgstr "What three conceits should you give up? "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.6"
msgid "Māno, omāno, atimāno—"
msgstr "Conceit, inferiority complex, and superiority complex. "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.7"
msgid "ime tayo mānā pahātabbā. "
msgstr "These are the three conceits you should give up. "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.8"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno imā tisso taṇhā pahīnā honti, ime ca tayo mānā; "
msgstr "When a mendicant has given up these three cravings and these three conceits "

msgctxt "an6.106:1.9"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu acchecchi taṇhaṃ, vivattayi saṃyojanaṃ, sammā mānābhisamayā antamakāsi dukkhassā”ti. "
msgstr "they’re called a mendicant who has cut off craving, untied the fetters, and by rightly comprehending conceit has made an end of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.106:1.10"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.106:1.11"
msgid "Ānisaṃsavaggo dasamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an6.106:2.1"
msgid "Pātubhāvo ānisaṃso, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an6.106:2.2"
msgid "aniccadukkhaanattato; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an6.106:2.3"
msgid "Nibbānaṃ anavatthi, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an6.106:2.4"
msgid "ukkhittāsi atammayo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an6.106:2.5"
msgid "Bhavā taṇhāyekā dasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an6.106:2.6"
msgid "Dutiyo paṇṇāsako samatto. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
